R1: ED Working Solution
Enzyme donor (microbial)-phenobarbital: 38 μg/l; chlorophenol red-β-D-galactopyranoside: 1.64 μg/l; anti-phenobarbital antibody (mouse monoclonal): 16.1 mg/l; 3-(N-morpholino) propanesulfonic acid (MOPS) buffer; buffer salts; preservative.
